          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", damaging not only the factory where Corvettes are made but also some of the National Corvette Museum Motorsports Park facilities. After dealing with the aftermath, the museum and its board of directors has announced it will upgrade the facilities instead of just restoring them, turning a bad situation into an opportunity.",
